pageProduct.name: Swisse Cranberry 25000mg 30 Capsules
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Swisse Ultiboost High Strength Cranberry is a premium quality formula to help support urinary tract health and provide symptomatic relief for medically diagnosed cystitis in a convenient, one-a-day dose.

Urinary Tract Health: Supports the health and function of the urinary tract, including bladder and kidney health. Cranberries possess anti-adhesion qualities.

Symptomatic Relief for Medically Diagnosed Cystitis: Provides symptomatic relief from discomfort associated with medically diagnosed cystitis such as itching, and frequent, burning urination.

Antioxidant Support: Cranberries are high in antioxidants, which help protect against free radical damage. Antioxidants also contribute to the maintenance of good health.

High Potency PACRAN®: Contains a unique powdered form of the whole cranberry fruit.

Size: 30 Capsules

Warnings

If symptoms persist consult your healthcare professional. If pain or irritation persists for more than 48 hours - consult your doctor. The presence of blood in the urine warrants immediate medical attention.

IMPORTANT INFORMATION

No added lactose, gluten, yeast, egg or artificial flavours.

Ingredients

Each capsule contains:

CRANBERRY (Vaccinium macrocarpon) powder equiv. fresh fruit 25 g

Directions

ADULT DOSAGE:

One capsule daily, during or immediately after a meal, or as directed by a healthcare professional.

USAGE INSTRUCTIONS

ADULT DOSAGE:

One capsule daily, during or immediately after a meal, or as directed by a healthcare professional.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25 degrees Celsius. Do not use if cap seal is broken.
